snippet.title: Starfire Soccer Challenge - Tryouts
snippet.description:
The tryout minigames are exactly the same as the drill practice minigames that you can access by clicking on the whistle icon.  The only differences are the banner on the field and the fact that the scores count towards which ending you get.

"The Starfire Soccer Challenge" is an English visual novel/sports game by the defunct game developer/publisher Purple Moon.  Originally planned to be the first in a series of soccer themed sports games for girls, only one game was released before Purple Moon was bought out by Mattel, who shelved plans for the series.
